      "text": "{user}さ～～ん！　お仕事\nお疲れ様でーす！　こころが癒やしてあげますよ～！",
      "startTime": 13.7939842796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり今日も来たな、こころ。癒やすだなんて言って\nまた何か企んで……って、うおぉ、恐竜ぅ！？",
      "startTime": 22.0333334605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_kaiju-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.9542158,
          "startTime": 23.4000000517
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "いけーい！　こころザウルス軍団とつげーーーーき！\n{user}さんをもぐもぐしちゃえ～！",
      "startTime": 30.7259189723,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "く、食われる……って、あれ、無事だ……\nあ、あの恐竜の群れは！？　どこへ消えた！？",
      "startTime": 38.9666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_kaiju-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 33.1333333333
    },
    {
