    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふっ、映像に決まってるじゃないですか！\nララさんの発明品で作った立体映像ですよー！",
      "startTime": 46.9263041613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_14_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "食べる一歩手前まで迫って驚かせる悪戯は\nモモちゃんのアイデアですけどね～！",
      "startTime": 54.492970828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
